          "ins_item_num": null,
          "ins_total": null,
          "f9": "The insurance report did not include step flashing, though INS line item 6 addresses pipe jack flashings separately. We are requesting 80 LF of step flashing. Step flashing is disturbed during the tear-off process and cannot be reused without compromising the weather-tight seal between the roof deck and the adjacent wall. Replacement of step flashing is a required component of a complete roofing scope and is distinct from the pipe jack flashings already included by the carrier. Please see the attached EagleView report confirming the measurements supporting this quantity.",
