          "f9": "The insurance report did not include a line item for counterflashing or apron flashing. We are requesting 30 LF of R&R counterflashing apron flashing. Apron flashing is disturbed during the tear-off process and cannot be reinstalled in a condition that maintains a proper weather-tight seal at the transition between the roof deck and adjacent walls or structures. Replacement is required as part of the standard roofing scope to ensure a watertight installation. Please see the attached EagleView report confirming the measurements supporting this quantity.",
